/// @author Minimal ERC1967 proxy by jtriley-eth (https://github.com/jtriley-eth/minimum-viable-proxy)
/// @dev Reduced version containing only ERC1967 proxy deployment functions.
library OptimisedLibClone {
    /*´:°•.°+.*•´.*:˚.°*.˚•´.°:°•.°•.*•´.*:˚.°*.˚•´.°:°•.°+.*•´.*:*/
    /*                       CUSTOM ERRORS                        */
